body: This IES files are circles which wasn't supported by IES>HB. I added them. Check the attached file for an example. It should support rectangular, sphere, and circle shapes. There might be other shapes that are not currently supported but it's not hard to add other primitive shapes if needed. You need to use the most updated version of Honeybee_Honeybee.
